{
  "texts": [
    "Raw text vs. discretized representationOne key aspect of the EvoLLM is our usage of discretized integer representations instead of raw floating point number strings.",
    "In preliminary experiments, we observed that the vocabulary tokenizer of LLMs struggles with representing high-precision numbers.",
    "Different numbers may result in different numbers of tokens (Figure 13), which in turn makes it challenging for the LLM to infer improvements.",
    "Most common tokenizers (e.g.",
    "SentencePiece) represent integer numbers up to 1000 as a single token."
  ]
}